<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Bella Varelis is a rumoured top-two contestant on this year's season of The Bachelor. </p>

<p>But an explosive trailer for Wednesday's rose ceremony suggests she could be sent home earlier than expected.</p>

<p>In the trailer, the marketing consultant, 25, accuses rival Irena Srbinovska of 'telling Locky what he wants to hear' before pulling the Bachelor aside.</p>

