<p>But Locky isn't impressed, telling producers: 'I am actually pretty upset. I have seen a side of Bella I didn't think I would see.'</p>

<p>At the rose ceremony, he is shown putting down his final rose and taking Bella outside for a chat as the other contestants look on.</p>

<p>Bold move! In the trailer, the marketing consultant, 25, accuses rival Irena of 'telling Locky what he wants to hear' before pulling the Bachelor aside</p>

